data.description: Charming Lakehead Retreat: This updated home sits on over 3 acres with a SEASONAL SPRING and offers a serene escape just MINUTES FROM THE LAKE! Open concept floorplan and expansive view windows provide an abundance of natural light. The stunning kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a stylish tiled backsplash, and abundant storage. Spacious primary bedroom boasts an ensuite bath plus 2 additional rooms with shared bath. Outside, the large paved back patio is shaded by beautiful trees, surrounded by mature landscaping, offering a delightful space for relaxation and entertaining. Large shop with two bays and a paved parking area add convenience, along with the attached two-car garage and a four-car carport provide room for all your toys!
